title.narrative: Operational support to the field offices

description.narrative: Operational support and oversight was provided to the 4 field offices to ensure greater efficiency and effectiveness. All operational needs from field offices were identified and addressed in a timely manner in coordination across all relevant units. We managed to suport Lease agreement negotiations for Dodoma and Mbeya Field Offices.;;We were able to set up;Zanzibar office in 2021.; The office continued;to assist on the coordination of work from home modalities while ensuring that the BCP locations remained functional and thereafter, the implementation of the return to office strategy which has now back to 80/100% on different locations. | Status:Met | As-of Date:13/12/2021
